The paper discusses the dissemination of research findings in HCI, which is a subfield of computer science. The focus is on the communication of research through mass media, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), social media (cs.SI), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and cybersecurity (cs.CY).
